OL,3,CSextortion: How AI is being used to
OL,4,Cblackmail children for money
OL,6,FAn increasing number of children and
OL,7,Fyoung people say they are becoming
OL,8,Fvictims of 'sextortion' in Guernsey.
OL,10,FThere have been double the number of
OL,11,Fpolice reports in the first nine
OL,12,Fmonths of the year, compared to the
OL,13,Fwhole of 2024.
OL,15,FWhile the coercion can involve real
OL,16,Fexplicit pictures, there is a growing
OL,17,Ftrend of artificial intelligence (AI)
OL,18,Fnow being used to create inappropriate
OL,19,Fphotos from non-sexual images, which
OL,20,Fare often taken from social media.
