OL,6,FThe manipulated pictures are then used
OL,7,Fto blackmail people for money, under
OL,8,Fthe threat that they will be released
OL,9,Fpublicly or to friends and family.
OL,11,FThe police say anyone can be affected,
OL,12,Fbut young men and boys appear to be
OL,13,Fthe main targets, with most reports
OL,14,Fmade by those aged between 14 and 30.
OL,16,FDigital Safety Development Officer
OL,17,FLaura Simpson says: "Sextortion is a
OL,18,Fcrime which is ultimately about money.
