OL,3,CSextortion: How AI is being used to
OL,4,Cblackmail children for money
OL,6,F"The criminals involved are not
OL,7,Ftechnologically sophisticated but know
OL,8,Fhow to emotionally manipulate victims
OL,9,Finto believing they have no choice but
OL,10,Fto pay up.
OL,12,F"This crime plays on the feelings of
OL,13,Fguilt and shame, which makes it easy
OL,14,Fto isolate teenagers."
OL,16,FNick Boughay, Police Schools Liaison
OL,17,FOfficer, is encouraging parents to
OL,18,Ftalk with their children about the
OL,19,Fdangers of this type of scam.
